 result←object caption arg
⍝ Read or change the caption of the APL session window

 :If 0=≢arg
     result←⎕SE.Caption ⍝ Return existing system caption
 :Else
     '∆WI DOMAIN ERROR: caption'##.##.Error (1≠≢arg)∨~##.##.IsChar 1⊃arg
     ⎕SE.Caption←1⊃arg ⍝ Change the system caption
     result←0 0⍴''
 :EndIf
